<td tEditID="c1r2" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r2" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<span id="docs-internal-guid-678969b4-a189-a0b9-0355-a0ba66473fe3"><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial">The NCS summer programme starts in less than a week, and we're aware that you still have not started your DBS application. </font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial">It is a legal requirement for all seasonal staff working on the NCS programme to have a valid DBS certificate. <b>If you do not have one, we will withdraw you from any waves you are placed on and you will not be entitled to compensation.</b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial"><b><br></b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial"><b>Already have a valid certificate?</b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial"><b><br></b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial">If you already have a DBS certificate, please first check it's valid. Your certificate needs to be:</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><ul><li><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Dated from <b>1st January 2015</b></span></font></li><li><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;">'Enhanced' (it will state this at the top)</span></font></li><li><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Children's Barred List checked (it should <b>not</b> say 'not requested')</span></font></li></ul><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;">If your certificate meets these requirements, please upload a <b>colour</b> scanned/photograhped copy of the whole certificate (front and back pages) to the <u><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/secure/EssentialInformation.aspx">Essential Information</a></u> page on your staffing portal.</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b>Need to apply for a new DBS?</b></span></font></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Follow <u><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/2016DBSinstructionspostoffer.pdf">these instructions</a></u> to apply for a new certificate through GB Group</span></font></li><li><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;">You'll need up to four forms of ID to hand</span></font></li><li><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;">DBS applications can take up to six weeks to process - please start your application as soon as possible and ensure you get your documents verified at the Post Office by <b>17th June</b> to avoid delays.</span></font></li></ul><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div></div><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b>Any questions?</b></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><b><br></b></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;">It's urgent that you get your DBS sorted as soon as possible to avoid missing out on work with summer. If you have any queries about the DBS application process, or your existing DBS certificate please get in touch with your local staffing team or contact us on seasonalroles@the-challenge.org. </span></font></div><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Best wishes,</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></font></div><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;">The Staffing Team</span></font></div><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; line-height: 20.24px; white-space: pre-wrap;">The Challenge</span></font></div></p></span>]]></td>
</tr>
